BEGIN_PGML
Convert the given interval notation into a number line graph and set-builder notation.

[`[$interval]`]

[_]{$gt}{1}

[@KeyboardInstructions('In set-builder notation:')@]**

[_]{$set_builder}{12}

END_PGML

############################################################
